Cars Toons is a series of American computer-animated short films by Pixar .
It features Lightning McQueen and Mater from Cars .
Larry the Cable Guy reprises his role as Mater while Keith Ferguson replaces Owen Wilson as Lightning McQueen -LRB- until The Radiator Springs 500 1/2 when Wilson reprises his role -RRB- .
The series ' first broadcast was on October 27 , 2008 on Toon Disney , Disney Channel , and ABC Family .
Not exclusive to television , some of those episodes have also premiered on DVDs / Blu-rays or as a theatrical short .